  personSpokenTo: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 41f6666ec8adc1846b1cc0f2bf100762, type: 2}
  lines:
  - "Hey there, sorry I couldn\u2019t talk last night, I was spending it chatting
    to the boss over messages."
  - "It\u2019s not often I get time to talk with friends nowadays, very little reason
    for me to do so with the family and all!"
  - But anyways, main thing I came to say, that same boss put me on to some crazy
    evidence about those rumours the other day.
  - Websites, documents the lot
  - "It\u2019s not often I get time to talk with friends nowadays, very little reason
    for me to do so with the family and all!"
